    "en": {
      "title": "Super Diesel - 40,000 tonnes of jet fuel will be released",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "A senior official of the Ministry of Energy said this afternoon (23) that a ship containing 30,000 metric tons of super diesel and 10,000 metric tons of aviation fuel has been paid for and the unloading of the fuel will begin tomorrow (24).",
        "The official said that it will take a few days for the fuel ship to reach the Sri Lankan sea border and also mentioned that the release was delayed due to a problem regarding the payment of money."
      ],
